OL,3,CHeatwave deaths: How extreme
OL,4,Ctemperatures can kill
OL,6,FIt's been estimated that almost 3,000
OL,7,Fpeople died from heat-related causes
OL,8,Fduring the hot weather in May and
OL,9,FJune, ITV News Health Correspondent
OL,10,FRebecca Barry reports
OL,12,FBritain's unprecedented June heatwave
OL,13,Ftriggered the country's first-ever run
OL,14,Fof three consecutive days of red
OL,15,Fextreme heat warnings, with the Met
OL,16,FOffice warning that conditions posed a
OL,17,F"high risk to life".
OL,19,FThose warnings were not merely
OL,20,Fprecautionary.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
