OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784112473
OL,3,CHeatwave deaths: How extreme
OL,4,Ctemperatures can kill
OL,6,FNew research, published on Monday,
OL,7,Fshows that 2,200 people died from heat-
OL,8,Frelated causes during June's record
OL,9,Fheatwaves across England and Wales.
OL,10,FCombined with figures from May, which
OL,11,Falso saw a heatwave, the total number
OL,12,Fof deaths stands at 2,750.
OL,14,FThe researchers say climate change has
OL,15,Fadded 3 to 4C to the hottest
OL,16,Ftemperatures, estimating that 42% died
OL,17,Fas a result of the "extra heat caused
OL,18,Fby human-induced warming".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
